Detailed Description

template<typename TYPE>
class isis::data::_internal::ValuePtrIterator< TYPE >

Basic iterator for ValuePtr.

This is a common iterator following the random access iterator model. It is not part of the reference counting used in ValuePtr. So make sure you keep the ValuePtr you created it from while you use this iterator.
